Test Organization Structure
├── Validation Functions (TestValidationFunctions)
├── Data Type Conversion (TestDataTypeConversion)  
├── Time Series Preparation (TestTimeSeriesPreparation)
├── Missing Data Handling (TestFillMissingWeeks)
├── Date Filtering (TestDateFiltering)
├── Data Merging (TestMergeAndFillAuthorData)
├── Data Analysis (TestGetIsbnsBeyondDate, TestGetBookSummary, etc.)
├── Utility Functions (TestUtilityFunctions)
├── Integration Scenarios (TestIntegrationScenarios)
├── Performance & Edge Cases (TestPerformanceAndEdgeCases)

# Key Test Coverage Highlights
1. Comprehensive Edge Cases:

Empty DataFrames
Missing required columns
Invalid date formats
Single row datasets
Large datasets (performance testing)

2. Data Quality Preservation:

Tests verify data integrity through transformations
Checks for unexpected null introduction
Validates data type conversions

3. Error Handling:

Proper exception raising and messages
Graceful handling of edge cases
Error propagation through function chains

4. Integration Scenarios:

End-to-end preprocessing chain testing
Realistic data scenarios
Data quality preservation checks

5. Performance Considerations:

Large dataset handling
Memory usage validation
Processing time assertions